pull_request.title: Fix appveyor test failures
pull_request.body: Appveyor installed a newer version of MSVC (from 19.26.28806.0 to 19.27.29111.0), which resulted in failures on the nightly build. This PR tweaks the picnic include files to accommodate this change.
